---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="About Me" description="Hi, I'm Alex Mak, a Full Stack Engineer." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<div class="card-container">
				<h1>About Me</h1>
				<div class="card-content">
					<p>
						Hi there! I'm <strong>Alex Mak</strong>, a passionate Full Stack Engineer. I love building robust and scalable web applications, tackling complex problems, and constantly learning new technologies.
					</p>
					<p>
						With experience across both frontend and backend development, I enjoy bringing ideas to life from conceptualization to deployment. Whether it's crafting intuitive user interfaces or designing efficient database architectures, I strive for excellence in every layer of the stack.
					</p>
					<p>
						Through this blog, I share my knowledge, experiences, and technical insights. Feel free to explore my articles and get in touch if you'd like to collaborate or simply chat about technology!
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
